title: Tootie's September 2014 Mix.flac
description:
Tootie's September 2014 Mix comes on the heels of OMGDDRBBQ and the 2014 Cleveland Dragon Boat Festival, and this unique mix is heavily influenced by both events. It starts off with an hour-long intermixed EDM set, portions of which will be the basis for a pre-dawn EDM set during Tootie's DJ stint at the Dragon Boat Festival, and some tracks of the set have been utilized in one of Cribstopper's Review mixes, who is the host of OMGDDRBBQ. Next is a selection of music in Dance Dance Revolution, the classic rhythm game which is the headline attraction of OMGDDRBBQ. It's also a sneak eavesdrop of content that will be included with the forthcoming major update to DDresampled - The Full Versions, which is creeping ever so closer to release. The mix ends with an EDM pairing, the latter of which is a track used in a Cribstopper Review mix.

The method focuses on vocal volume.
